{"tid":1393743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曬氣啦，8月5罷工有柒用","createTime":"2019-08-01T07:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:15:43.000Z","uid":176598,"like":81,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4766f532b0c080eed20fd7bb8609171b30187bae","tid":1393743,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:42:39.000Z","msg":"罷一日工係冇乜用，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5一定要罷一日</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n聽埋先走！<br />\n<br />\n眼見前線咁多人受傷同被捕，你話心痛，你話反對暴力，你話一個都不能少，依家就比你一個最和平但最有殺傷力嘅方法，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無限期三罷</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n三罷已經講咗好耐，但喺香港呢個自私自利嘅社會，一直都實行唔到。今次係想討論下點樣增加三罷嘅可能性: 主要探討點樣<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">凝聚自己機構入面嘅抗爭力量</span></span></ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n大家都希望三罷之餘可以保障到自己，成間公司得自己罷肯定大大穫。所以，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5號係試水温同相認嘅大日子</span></span></strong>，大家只需按合約合理地請一日假，就可以同公司同路人相認，可以試到你地適唔適合參加日後嘅無限期罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>相認方法(自行判斷邊個方法最適合自己)</strong></span></span><br />\n1 最簡單安全就係睇翻公司嘅缺席記錄<br />\n2 sd mass email交代自己請咗假，有咩事再跟進之類<br />\n3 開公司罷工tg group，驚可以用太空卡入group，入group show職員證<br />\n4 相約罷工當日12點喺公司樓下(非當眼處)集合，再一齊參加工作嗰區嘅罷工集會，緊記準時<br />\n5 等你留言<br />\n<br />\n相認之後，你地就好似一個小型工會，靠參與人數同參與人喺公司嘅地位同公司bargain。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要公司冇咗你地呢班人會瀨嘢，咁你地就成功。</span></strong></span>如果你地有信心，甚至可以嘗試說服公司帶起罷市，如果唔得就你地自己罷工，佢都已經好難運作。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係冇人同你相認，或你地人數不足，唔緊要，請你地繼續大大力支持其他抗爭活動。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢到強烈要求大家豁出去，因為前線已經犧牲生命同前途！！請大家只最低限度咁保障自己生存，生存只需食物，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你冇咗份工唔會餓死嘅，請你唔好再顧慮咁多！！</span></strong></span>如果你覺得三罷會影響你前途，你諗下如果今鋪香港人輸咗，你仲可以有咩前途？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果你再唔行動，你只係温水裡嘅青蛙，遲早仼人宰割！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，繼續大大力宣傳8.5三罷！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WMuNuW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WMuNuW.png&h=aabd45b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5HhWou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5HhWou.png&h=a6b0dca6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"156d877c20c6bdbcbda2b64e984473f4d45ef6e2","tid":1393743,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:52:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb523ca5527445c70ddcf91fecc2770909b9977b","tid":1393743,"uid":243182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5927fb58e05cc126019c5b410486ac97c23a4de","tid":1393743,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:03:01.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"2e95467d14ef12f1004f4946cf0460e76fc1ce43","tid":1393743,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"罷一日冇用，要罷佢老母一直罷"},{"pid":"f4ebbd81b4a9d1dd8eb650a7001f6d54dfccfb62","tid":1393743,"uid":243182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a634387094aaff62931d2bf236d1e719dec7a52","tid":1393743,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33290947dbbf2abeeb23fbf8c4efcc7fe03aaddf","tid":1393743,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"支持無限期罷工<br />\n光復香港"},{"pid":"1d5c9afdcb8852d97276737911ec190111e2ee87","tid":1393743,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"[85罷工] 齊齊入返自己行業tg gr